<h1>Delete Your Explain AI Account</h1>

<p>
If you would like to permanently delete your Explain AI account and associated data, you may do so using one of the following methods.
</p>

<h2>Option 1 (Recommended)</h2>

<p>
Open the Explain AI app and navigate to:
</p>

<p><strong>Profile → Settings → Delete Account</strong></p>

<p>
Follow the prompts to permanently delete your account.
</p>

<h2>Option 2</h2>

<p>
If you cannot access your account, contact us by email and request account deletion.
</p>

<p>
<strong>Email:</strong> cartercarroyt@gmail.com
</p>

<h2>What is Deleted?</h2>

<ul>
<li>Your account information</li>
<li>Your saved flashcards</li>
<li>Your study decks</li>
<li>Your learning history</li>
<li>Your favorites</li>
<li>Your profile information</li>
</ul>

<h2>What May Be Retained?</h2>

<p>
Certain information may be retained when required by law or for fraud prevention purposes.
</p>

